titles.title: Electing Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

term.name: House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform

bill.summary: 1/28/2009--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Elects certain named Majority Members to the House Committees on Homeland Security and on Oversight and Government Reform.
